    "service.electromagnetic-calculations.title": "Electromagnetic Calculations",
    "service.electromagnetic-calculations.desc": "We perform detailed electromagnetic calculations including impedance evaluation, no-load and load losses, short-circuit forces, and winding temperature rise estimation. Our calculations follow IEC and IEEE methodologies and are validated through extensive FEM simulations to ensure accuracy and reliability.",
