    "service.tank-and-external-equipment.desc": "We design transformer tanks, conservators, radiators, and all external structural components. Our approach integrates structural FEM analysis with thermal considerations to produce optimized designs that are cost-effective to manufacture, easy to transport, and reliable in service.",
