    "service.fem-simulations.title": "FEM Simulations",
    "service.fem-simulations.desc": "Our FEM simulation services provide detailed numerical analysis for electromagnetic, structural, thermal, and electrostatic problems in transformer design. Using advanced software tools, we deliver accurate predictions of real-world behavior to validate designs before manufacturing.",
    "service.static-structural.title": "Static Structural",
    "service.static-structural.desc": "Static structural FEM analysis evaluates mechanical stresses and deformations in transformer components under normal operating conditions, transportation loads, and short-circuit forces. We assess tank walls, clamping structures, core frames, and winding supports to ensure mechanical integrity.",
    "service.harmonic-response.title": "Harmonic Response",
    "service.harmonic-response.desc": "Harmonic response analysis determines how transformer structures respond to periodic excitation at various frequencies. This is critical for assessing vibration levels, noise emissions, and potential resonance issues that could affect transformer reliability and compliance with noise regulations.",
    "service.magnetic-fields.title": "Magnetic Fields",
    "service.magnetic-fields.desc": "Magnetic field FEM simulations model the distribution of magnetic flux in and around the transformer, identifying areas of high leakage flux, stray losses, and localized heating. These analyses are essential for optimizing shielding, reducing hot spots, and validating impedance calculations.",
    "service.electrostatic.title": "Electrostatic",
    "service.electrostatic.desc": "Electrostatic FEM analysis evaluates electric field distributions within transformer insulation systems. We identify critical stress points, optimize clearances and creepage distances, and verify that insulation structures withstand lightning impulse, switching impulse, and applied voltage tests per IEC 60076.",
    "service.materials-specifications.title": "Materials Specifications",
    "service.materials-specifications.desc": "We develop comprehensive materials specifications for all transformer components — from electrical steels and copper conductors to insulating oils and solid insulation materials. Our specifications ensure consistent quality, compliance with international standards, and optimized procurement across your supply chain.",
    "service.condition-assessment.title": "Condition Assessment Services",
    "service.condition-assessment.desc": "Our condition assessment services provide a thorough evaluation of transformer health using diagnostic testing, oil analysis, and visual inspection. We deliver actionable reports with risk assessments and recommendations for maintenance, refurbishment, or replacement to optimize your asset management strategy.",
    "service.dga-and-oil-analysis.title": "DGA and Oil Analysis",
    "service.dga-and-oil-analysis.desc": "Dissolved gas analysis (DGA) and oil quality testing are fundamental diagnostic tools for assessing transformer condition. We interpret DGA results using multiple methods (Duval Triangle, Rogers Ratios, IEC 60599) and provide clear assessments of fault types, severity, and recommended actions.",
    "service.modernization-and-refurbishment.title": "Modernization and Refurbishment",
    "service.modernization-and-refurbishment.desc": "We provide engineering support for transformer modernization and refurbishment projects, including redesign of active parts, upgrade of cooling systems, replacement of bushings and tap changers, and installation of modern monitoring systems to extend service life and improve performance.",
    "service.reverse-engineering.title": "Reverse Engineering",
    "service.reverse-engineering.desc": "Our reverse engineering service recreates complete technical documentation from existing transformers when original drawings are unavailable. We perform detailed measurements, material analysis, and electromagnetic calculations to produce accurate design data for spare parts, refurbishment, or replication.",
    "service.active-parts-inspection.title": "Active Parts Inspection",
    "service.active-parts-inspection.desc": "We conduct thorough inspections of transformer active parts (core and windings) during manufacturing, refurbishment, or failure investigation. Our engineers assess workmanship quality, dimensional accuracy, insulation condition, and compliance with design specifications and international standards.",
    "service.maintenance-planning.title": "Maintenance Planning",
    "service.maintenance-planning.desc": "Our maintenance planning services help utilities and industrial operators develop optimized maintenance strategies for their transformer fleets. We consider asset condition, criticality, loading patterns, and failure statistics to create cost-effective plans that balance reliability with budget constraints.",
    "service.life-cycle-planning.title": "Life Cycle Planning",
    "service.life-cycle-planning.desc": "Life cycle planning provides a strategic view of your transformer fleet over its entire operational life. We model aging mechanisms, predict end-of-life timelines, and develop investment strategies for replacement and refurbishment that minimize total cost of ownership while maintaining grid reliability.",
    "service.specification-writing-and-review.title": "Specification Writing and Review",
    "service.specification-writing-and-review.desc": "We write and review transformer procurement specifications to ensure they are technically complete, unambiguous, and aligned with international standards. Our specifications cover all critical aspects including performance requirements, testing protocols, quality assurance, and delivery conditions.",
    "service.factory-audits.title": "Factory Audits",
    "service.factory-audits.desc": "Our factory audit service evaluates transformer manufacturing facilities against international quality standards and best practices. We assess production processes, quality management systems, testing capabilities, and staff competency to help you qualify suppliers and mitigate procurement risks.",
    "service.proposal-evaluation.title": "Proposal Evaluation",
    "service.proposal-evaluation.desc": "We provide independent technical evaluation of transformer manufacturer proposals, comparing designs against specifications, assessing cost-effectiveness, and identifying potential risks. Our evaluations help procurement teams make informed decisions based on objective technical criteria.",
    "service.transformer-design-review.title": "Transformer Design Review",
    "service.transformer-design-review.desc": "Our design review service provides independent verification of transformer designs before manufacturing begins. We check electromagnetic calculations, thermal performance, mechanical strength, insulation coordination, and compliance with specifications and standards to identify potential issues early.",
    "service.independent-inspection.title": "Independent Inspection and Test Witnessing",
    "service.independent-inspection.desc": "We provide independent inspection and test witnessing services at transformer manufacturing facilities worldwide. Our engineers verify that manufacturing quality and test results comply with purchase specifications, approved drawings, and applicable IEC/IEEE standards.",
    "service.core-and-coil-inspection.title": "Core and Coil Inspection",
    "service.core-and-coil-inspection.desc": "Dedicated inspection of transformer core and coil assemblies during the manufacturing process. We verify core lamination quality, winding dimensions, insulation build-up, lead routing, and overall workmanship against approved design documents and industry best practices.",
    "service.pre-processing-inspection.title": "Pre-processing Inspection",
    "service.pre-processing-inspection.desc": "Pre-processing inspection verifies the quality of materials and components before they enter the transformer assembly process. We check incoming materials, semi-finished parts, and sub-assemblies against specifications to prevent quality issues from propagating into the final product.",
    "service.pre-tanking-inspection.title": "Pre-tanking Inspection",
